50 people killed in Peru - Indigenous people demanding their rights - their voices are not terrorists. After 500 years we are still here - struggling - we are visible. We protect our water, our trees, our language. We are the original environmentalist. We protect Pachamama. When Tupac Amaru II was executed he said “I promise to return, and I will be millions”. The protests in Peru right now is a reflection of our ancestry, we demand Justice. The violence against my people now needs to end KACHKANIRAQMI 🏳️‍🌈
